---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Terms of service \u2014 Harmony Threads" description="The terms that apply when you buy from Harmony Threads.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl">Terms</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-paper/80 leading-relaxed">
      <p>By placing an order with Harmony Threads you agree to the following, plain-English terms.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">Orders & pricing</h2>
      <p>All prices are in GBP (\u00a3) and include UK VAT where applicable. We reserve the right to cancel and refund any order with a pricing or stock error before dispatch.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>All artwork, writing, imagery and audio on this site is the property of Harmony Threads and its contributors. You can read, view, and enjoy \u2014 not redistribute or resell.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">Governing law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
